{"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/slothcreator\/gettingstarted"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"role":"article","roleHeading":"Article","modules":[{"name":"SlothCreator"}],"title":"Getting Started with Sloths","images":[{"type":"card","identifier":"gettingStarted-card.png"}]},"abstract":[{"text":"Create a sloth and assign personality traits and abilities.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator"]]},"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Essentials","anchor":"Essentials","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/SlothySample","doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth"],"generated":true}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Sloths are complex creatures that require careful creation and a suitable habitat. After creating a sloth, you’re responsible for feeding them, providing fulfilling activities, and giving them opportunities to exercise and rest.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Every sloth has a "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/name"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/color-swift.property"},{"type":"text","text":". You can optionally provide a "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/power-swift.property"},{"type":"text","text":" if your sloth has special supernatural abilities."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"slothPower.png","type":"image"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Create a Sloth","anchor":"Create-a-Sloth"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To create a standard sloth without any special supernatural powers, you initialize a new instance of the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth"},{"text":" structure, and supply a name and a color, as the following code shows:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["var sloth = Sloth(name: \"Super Sloth\", color: .blue, power: .none)"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If your sloth possesses one of the special powers of ","type":"text"},{"code":"ice","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"fire","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"wind","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", or ","type":"text"},{"code":"lightning","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", you can specify this at creation:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["var superSloth = Sloth(name: \"Silly Sloth\", color: .green, power: .lightning)"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you’re creating a large number of sloths, you can define your own random name generator that conforms to the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/NameGenerator","type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol, and use it to generate names:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["let slothNamer = MyCustomSlothNamer()","var sloths: [Sloth] = []","","for _ in 0...100 {","    let name = slothNamer.generateName(seed: 0)","    var sloth = Sloth(name: name, color: .green, power: .ice)","    ","    sloths.append(sloth)","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Provide a Habitat","anchor":"Provide-a-Habitat"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sloths thrive in comfortable habitats. To create a sloth-friendly habitat, you specify whether it’s humid, warm, or both. The following listing creates a habitat that’s humid and warm, which results in a high "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Habitat\/comfortLevel"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["let lovelyHabitat = Habitat(isHumid: true, isWarm: true)"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"After you create a sloth habitat, you’re ready for sloths to sleep in it. Sleeping in a habitat increases the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/energyLevel","isActive":true},{"text":" of the sloth by the comfort level of the habitat. Sloths sleep for long periods so, by default, your sloth sleeps for 12 hours, but you can also customize this value:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["superSloth.sleep(in: lovelyHabitat)","hyperSloth.sleep(in: lovelyHabitat, for: 2)"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Exercise a Sloth","anchor":"Exercise-a-Sloth"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To keep your sloths happy and fulfilled, you can create activities for them to perform. Define your activities by conforming to the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol and implementing the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity\/perform(with:)","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" method:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["struct Sightseeing: Activity {","    func perform(with sloth: inout Sloth) -> Speed {","        sloth.energyLevel -= 10","        return .slow","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Feed a Sloth","anchor":"Feed-a-Sloth"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sloths require sustenance to perform activities, so you can feed them "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/Food"},{"type":"text","text":". Standard sloth food includes leaves and twigs:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["superSloth.eat(.largeLeaf)","hyperSloth.eat(.twig)"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Schedule Care for a Sloth","anchor":"Schedule-Care-for-a-Sloth"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To make it easy to care for your sloth, SlothCreator provides a ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/CareSchedule","type":"reference"},{"text":" structure that lets you define activities or foods for your sloth to enjoy at specific times. Create the schedule, then provide a tuple of a ","type":"text"},{"code":"Date","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and an ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity","type":"reference"},{"text":", or you can use some of the standard care procedures:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["let events: [(Date, CareSchedule.Event)] = [","    (Date.now, .bedtime),","    (Date(timeIntervalSinceNow: 12*60*60), .breakfast),","    (Date(timeIntervalSinceNow: 13*60*60), .activity(Sightseeing()))","]","","let schedule = CareSchedule(events: events)","superSloth.schedule = schedule"],"syntax":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/GettingStarted"},"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"references":{"slothCreator-icon.png":{"identifier":"slothCreator-icon.png","alt":"A technology icon representing the SlothCreator framework.","type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/SlothCreator\/slothCreator-icon@2x.png","traits":["2x","light"]}]},"slothPower.png":{"alt":"A diagram with the five sloth power types: ice, fire, wind, lightning, and none.","variants":[{"traits":["2x","light"],"url":"\/images\/SlothCreator\/slothPower@2x.png"},{"traits":["2x","dark"],"url":"\/images\/SlothCreator\/slothPower~dark@2x.pn